data.description:
Multiple Lease Terms are Available. A cozy, spacious open floor plan 3-bd 2-bth ranch style home centrally located in Huntsville, AL. It comes with a dedicated workspace (perfect for working remote) with great amenities to include Wi-Fi, a security system, and a two-car garage for private parking. The kitchen includes Stainless steel appliances, to include gas stove, Keurig Coffee Maker, pots, pans, utensils, plates, bowls, potholders, and kitchen towels. All Bedrooms are fully stocked with bed linens. Bathrooms are stocked with bath towels and hairdryers. Washer and dryer provided. HD 50" TV in the Living room. Rent Includes Wi-Fi and Lawn Care. Easy access to HWY 72. Located in the Buckhorn School District, and 10 mins away from downtown Huntsville.

Owner will pay internet and lawn care. No pets allowed. This home is currently being used as an Airbnb. Month to Month lease terms and long-term leases are available. This home is perfect for corporate rental or if you're needing a place to stay while waiting for a home to be built. An unfurnished option is available for less rent. 

Credentials are as follows:
1. The monthly NET income amount must equal three times the monthly rent. 
2. Must have maintained current employment for a minimum of six months. 
3. Minimum credit score 590. 
4. No Eviction, Criminal Record, or Bankruptcy. 
5. Anyone 18 years or older who will be living in the property for any length of time is required to fill out a rental application. 
6. We do not accept section 8 vouchers. 

**We will never accept payment over the phone/internet/wire before signing a lease and meeting you in person at the property. If you're communicating with someone about this property, asking you to pay upfront, and you haven't personally met a property manager at the property, you're being scammed. We are not responsible for false advertising and money sent to scammers through false advertising. Every rental property listed online is being duplicated by scammers.**
